<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="02 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a">我問你，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你敢吃甜食嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我從小就不太喜歡，<delay40 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以幾乎沒有吃過<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x3 0x4 0x5" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">對了，前陣子有個老朋友<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />送了個叫什麼「馬卡龍」的玩意給我。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後啊，<delay8 />我試吃了一口，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />發現味道還挺不賴啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay8 />這種東西偶爾吃吃，<delay8 />
應該也不錯吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">對了，前陣子<delay8 />
有個老朋友邀我去吃<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一種叫什麼「聖代」的東西。
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />又甜<delay8 />又冰，<delay8 />還讓我頭痛，<delay20 />
嚇了我一大跳。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay8 />這種東西偶爾吃一次，<delay8 />
應該也不錯吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">對了，前陣子有個老朋友<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />送了「麵包乾」這種玩意給我。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我從來沒吃過這個，<delay8 />但還是冒著<delay20 />
可能是甜食的風險勉強嘗試，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />發現香香脆脆，其實還挺不錯吃啊！
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay8 />這種東西偶爾吃一點，<delay8 />
應該也不錯吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 03 01 00 00 00 0a">我問你，<delay40 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />晴天跟雨天，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你比較喜歡哪一種？</message>
	<message label="007_a" attrib="08 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">晴天</message>
	<message label="007_b" attrib="09 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">雨天</message>
	<message label="007_c" attrib="0a 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">陰天</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">其實我啊，<delay8 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是個「陽光男」喔！<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每到關鍵時刻，<delay8 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />天氣<delay8 />總是會放晴！
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像是遠足、運動會之類的前一天晚上，<delay8 />
就在心裡想著我吧！<pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />隔天說不定<delay8 />就會放晴囉！<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～哈哈！</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喔，<delay20 />原來<delay8 />你喜歡雨啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還挺有詩意的嘛！<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我原本以為<delay8 />會喜歡雨的，
頂多就只有青蛙跟蝸牛罷了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能像你這樣<delay8 />
斬釘截鐵地<delay8 />說自己喜歡雨的人，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我可不討厭喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喜歡陰天嗎<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看你這樣子<delay8 />
也不像是在說笑。
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我這人就是直腸子性格，<delay8 />
所以有時候會不小心說出傷人的話<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是看來在你心中，<delay20 />
有著能夠接納一切的溫柔吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="0d 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然<delay8 />這個世界發展得越來越方便，<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我有時候不禁會想：<delay8 />
只追求方便，真的好嗎<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0xe 0xf 0x10" /></message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比方說計算機！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我還是堅持用算盤！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />敲響算珠的觸感，<delay8 />還有清脆悅耳的撞擊聲！<delay40 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種樂趣，<delay8 />數位產品可辦不到吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把算盤當成直排輪滑，<delay20 />
然後被狠狠訓一頓……<delay8 />這種刺激感，<delay8 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />用計算機可體會不到吧！？<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～哈哈！</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比方說郵件！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我還是堅持手寫信件！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一字一句<delay8 />都由自己親筆<delay8 />全神貫注地寫下，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才能更確切地傳達心意！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我的字不好看，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是至少也要把心意傳達給對方！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比如說衛生紙！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我還是堅持用抹布！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只是稍微灑出一點水，<delay8 />
可能會讓人想拿衛生紙來擦，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但你不覺得那樣很浪費嗎？
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />抹布就不一樣了，<delay8 />能夠反覆使用，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不用擔心浪費，反而還比較方便！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="12 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這麼說來，<delay20 />你知道嗎？</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x13 0x14 0x15" /></message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />被稱為「海中牛奶」的生蠔，<delay20 />
可是含有<delay8 />1000mg以上的
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />牛磺酸喔！？
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當你急需精力<delay20 />的時候，<delay8 />
應該很有用吧！<delay20 /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～哈哈！</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />又濃又甜～的蜂蜜，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像會因為成分跟含水量，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以<delay8 />不會腐壞耶！？
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過啊，<delay8 /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我不喜歡吃甜食，<delay20 />
所以跟我無關啦！<delay20 /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～哈哈！</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />刨冰的糖漿啊，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />似乎只是顏色跟氣味不同而已，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />草莓口味和哈密瓜口味<delay8 />據說嚐起來都一樣！？
<anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過腦袋會刺痛，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />跟口味<delay8 />沒關係就是了！<delay20 /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～哈哈！</message>
	<message label="023" attrib="18 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我問你，<delay8 />你有碰過<delay20 />
「電腦」這玩意嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我之前<delay8 />第一次<delay20 />
在死黨家裡碰到，<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />該怎麼說才好啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
那些專門用語搞得我好亂啊！</message>
	<message label="024" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x19 0x1a 0x1b" /></message>
	<message label="025" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />死黨要我<delay20 />
「總之先試著打開電腦」，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我根本不知道他在說什麼啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />差點要拆了電腦<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />害我被他笑！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="026" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後死黨又叫我<delay20 />「用滑鼠點兩下」，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我還是聽不懂他在說什麼啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就抓起連在電腦上的那個小東西<delay20 />
敲畫面，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果他大吃一驚，急忙拉住我了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="027" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最後他說<delay20 />「試試看拖曳跟放下」，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我始終都無法理解他在說什麼啊。
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想應該是<delay8 />「抬起來放下」……<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是當我抬起電腦的時候，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />他就一臉鐵青地攔住我了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="030" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="030_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你知道現在的<tag a="110" b="33" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最需要的<delay8 />到底是什麼嗎！？<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就是……<delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能夠當機立斷的領袖！<pageBreak />要說有什麼人夠資格當這座島的領袖嘛<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那肯定就是本大爺了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了幫助我登上這座島的頂點，<delay frames="30" />
你想跟其他人講幾個凸顯我這個人<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />鶴立雞群的故事也行喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="030_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就聽我說件往事吧！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以前曾經有個傳聞<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說我挖到了不得了的財寶<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我根本沒印象，所以還很慌張咧。<delay40 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果仔細調查後<delay8 />才發現那個傳聞
原只是在講<delay8 />我挖出了小時候埋在土裡的彈珠。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />傳聞還真有趣對吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從小事開始越傳越誇張，<delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最後連彈珠都傳成金銀財寶了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>